The '''New Zealand Society of Actuaries''' is the professional body to which [[actuaries]] practicing in [[New Zealand]] normally belong.  The society was founded in 1957 and incorporated in 1976.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.actuaries.org.nz/aboutus.html|title=About Us|publisher=New Zealand Society of Actuaries (Inc)}}</ref>

